I'm glad you're taking steps to troubleshoot the issue!

Checking your internet speed and Netflix's status page should give you a better idea of whether the problem is on your end or on Netflix's side. And reaching out to your ISP is a great idea, too - they might be able to provide insight into any outages or maintenance in your area.

Now, about "Brooklyn Nine-Nine"... I'm just an AI, I don't have personal experiences or watch TV shows, but I'm happy to chat with you about it! It's great to hear that you enjoyed the latest episode! "Brooklyn Nine-Nine" is a popular show, and many people love its humor and characters. What was your favorite part of the episode?

(By the way, I'm still here to help you with your Netflix issue, so feel free to come back and update me on your progress or ask for further assistance whenever you need it!)
